frus:attachment.p:
Invoice of cargo for Sea Bride, Charles F. White, master, consigned;
                                Henry Spaulding, supercargo on board, to proceed to Cape Town;
                                transact the business according to memorandum, using despatch for
                                the vessel, and consigning all proceeds of sales and advances, with
                                remainder of cargo, to Wm. E. Hines, the shipper agent at
                                Zanzibar.
